Release 0.6.0 - 2016/6/21

* Dependencies
  1. Update Scala version from 2.10.4, 2.11.5 to 2.10.6, 2.11.7.
  2. Update fluent-logger from 0.3.1 to 0.3.2.
  3. Update slf4j-api and slf4j-simple from 1.7.10 to 1.7.13.
  4. Update json4s-native from 3.2.11 to 3.3.0.

* Bug fixes
  1. Fix to return false if it exceeds the buffer capacity.

* Misc
  1. Refactor code.

Release 0.5.1 - 2015/1/17

* Big fixes
  1. Reconnect to fluentd servers at flush() correctly(Contributed by @anekos).
  2. Flush buffers when closing.

Release 0.5.0

* Deprecated scala 2.9.x support.
* Refactoring tests.

Release 0.4.0

* Using json as serialization format instead of msgpack-scala.

Release 0.3.0 - 2013/1/13

* Scala native class support(basic collections/options).

Release 0.2.0 - 2012/11/12

* Changed to use fluent-logger-java
* Added tests.

Release 0.1.0 - 2011/11/03

* First version
